script.name: plugin.autotrade.getroute.short
script.description: ST LT UT: Get best trade route
script.sourceplaintext:
* SymTec (19-03-09) * V2: Cycrow, 2018/06/19 * - Adjusted to use tables * ====================================
@ = wait randomly from 3500 to 7500 ms
* constants $flags = [Find.Known] | [Find.Friend] | [Find.Neutral] | [Find.DockingAllowed] | [Find.Multiple] $list = table alloc
if $experience >= 5 @ $blacklist = [THIS] -> call script plugin.autotrade.blacklistsector : Add Sector=null Is Local=[FALSE] else $blacklist = table alloc end
* find buystations $stations = find station in galaxy: startsector=$startsector class or type=Factory race=null flags=$flags refobj=[THIS] serial=null max.jumps=$range num=50 if $experience >= 3 gosub add.docks end $station.i = size of array $stations $sector.allowed = table alloc while $station.i dec $station.i = $station = $stations[$station.i] $sector = $station -> get sector if $blacklist[$station] remove element from array $stations at index $station.i continue end if $blacklist[$sector] remove element from array $stations at index $station.i continue end if $station -> only player own ships can trade with remove element from array $stations at index $station.i continue end
if not $sector.allowed[$sector] @ if not [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.checkvalidroute : Destination Sector=$sector Allow Target=[FALSE] Command Rejected Sound=[FALSE] $blacklist[$sector] = [TRUE] @ = wait 10 ms remove element from array $stations at index $station.i continue end $sector.allowed[$sector] = [TRUE] end
$products = $station -> get products $product.i = size of array $products while $product.i dec $product.i = $ware = $products[$product.i] skip if [THIS] -> can transport ware $ware continue $price = $station -> get price of ware $ware $price2 = get average price of ware $ware do if $price > $price2 continue
@ do if [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.lockstation : Station=$station Ware=$ware Check Only?=[TRUE] Remove?=[FALSE] continue
$amount = $station -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay
$ware.array = $list[$ware] if $ware.array $p = $ware.array[0] $a = $ware.array[1] if ( $price < $p ) OR ( $price == $p AND $amount > $a ) $ware.array[0] = $price $ware.array[1] = $amount $ware.array[2] = $station end else $ware.array = create new array, size=3, elements=$price, $amount, $station, null, null, null, null, null $list[$ware] = $ware.array end end end
skip if size of table $list return null
* find sellstations $buystation = null $sellstation = null $tradeware = null $maxprofit = 0
$key = get next key: table=$list key=null
while $key $ware = $key $key = get next key: table=$list key=$key $price = $list[$ware][0] $amount = $list[$ware][1] $station = $list[$ware][2]
$volume = get volume of ware $ware do if $amount * $volume > $freecargo $amount = $freecargo / $volume
* set average price inc $price = $price2 = get average price of ware $ware do if $price < $price2 AND $experience < 15 $price = $price2
* find station $sector.allowed = table alloc while [TRUE] $station2 = find station: resource $ware with best price: min.price=$price, amount=$amount, max.jumps=$sellrange, startsector=$startsector, trader=[THIS], exclude array=$blacklist if not $station2 $station2 = find station: resource $ware with best price: min.price=$price, amount=1, max.jumps=$sellrange, startsector=$startsector, trader=[THIS], exclude array=$blacklist end skip if $station2 break $bl.sector = $station2 -> get sector if not $sector.allowed[$bl.sector] @ if not [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.checkvalidroute : Destination Sector=$bl.sector Allow Target=[FALSE] Command Rejected Sound=[FALSE] $blacklist[$bl.sector] = $bl.sector @ = wait 10 ms continue end $sector.allowed[$bl.sector] = $bl.sector end
@ if [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.lockstation : Station=$station2 Ware=$ware Check Only?=[TRUE] Remove?=[FALSE] $blacklist[$station2] = $station2 @ = wait 10 ms continue end do if $station2 -> exists break @ = wait 1 ms end
skip if $station2 continue
* get tradeable amount $amount2 = $station2 -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay do if $amount2 < $amount $amount = $amount2 $amount2 = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay do if $ware == Energy Cells OR $ware == Fighter Drone $amount2 = 0
$price = $list[$ware][0] $price2 = $station2 -> get price of ware $ware $profit = $amount * ( $price2 - $price ) + $amount2 * $price2 if $profit > $maxprofit * distance weight $sector = $station -> get sector $jump1 = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $sector $jump2 = $station2 -> get sector $jump2 = get jumps from sector $sector to sector $jump2
$profit = $profit / ( $jump1 + $jump2 + 1 ) if $profit > $maxprofit $buystation = $station $sellstation = $station2 $tradeware = $ware $maxprofit = $profit end end end
* reserve station spots, prepare return values $ret = null @ if [THIS] -> call script plugin.autotrade.checksector : Startstation=$buystation Targetstation=$sellstation if $experience >= 11 @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.autotrade.blacklistsector : Add Sector=$buystation Is Local=[FALSE] @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.autotrade.blacklistsector : Add Sector=$sellstation Is Local=[FALSE] end $ret = create new array, arguments=$buystation, $sellstation, $tradeware, $profit, null end
@ = wait randomly from 200 to 500 ms return $ret
add.docks: * Add docks to list $flags = [Find.Known] | [Find.Friend] | [Find.Neutral] | [Find.DockingAllowed] | [Find.Multiple] $docks = find station in galaxy: startsector=$startsector class or type=Dock race=null flags=$flags refobj=[THIS] serial=null max.jumps=$range num=20 $station.i = size of array $docks while $station.i dec $station.i = $station = $docks[$station.i] $sector = $station -> get sector do if $blacklist[$station] continue do if $blacklist[$sector] continue do if $station -> only player own ships can trade with continue append $station to array $stations end endsub return null
